<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Rules</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 50px auto;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 40px;
            text-align: left;
            transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out;
        }

        .container:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }

        h1 {
            color: #343a40;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 32px;
        }

        p {
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        ol {
            list-style-type: decimal;
            padding-left: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        li {
            font-size: 16px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: #6c757d;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .back-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .back-btn:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }

        @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                padding: 20px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Rules</h1>
        <p>Here are the rules for the quiz:</p>
        <ol>
            <li>Each question has four options.</li>
            <li>Select the correct answer from the options.</li>
            <li>After selecting an answer, click the "Next" button to proceed to the next question.</li>
            <li>Once you've answered all questions, click the "Submit" button to see your score.</li>
        </ol>
        <a href="/quiz_homepage" class="back-btn">Back to Quiz</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
